@startuml
title Multiple Parallel Journeys — Rendering & Deduplication

actor Clinician
participant "JourneyTab\n(CaseDetail UI)" as JT
participant "PatientCareplan\n(PatientView UI)" as PC
participant "client/\npatientJourneys" as Client
participant "service/\njourneyResolver" as Resolver
participant "getEffectiveSteps" as GES
participant "getMergedDueSteps\nForPatient" as MDS

== Clinician view (CaseDetail / JourneyTab) ==

Clinician -> JT : Open case detail\n(journeys tab)
JT -> Client : getPatientJourneys(patientId)
Client --> JT : PatientJourney[]\n(e.g. wrist + hip programmes)
JT -> JT : Sort journeys:\n  ACTIVE → SUSPENDED → COMPLETED\n  newest-first within group
JT -> JT : Render MUI Tabs\n  Tab 1: "Handled Radius (ACTIVE)"\n  Tab 2: "Höft (ACTIVE)"\n  ...
Clinician -> JT : Click tab for journey N
JT -> Client : getEffectiveSteps(journeyId_N)
Client -> GES : getEffectiveSteps(journey)
GES -> GES : Apply totalPauseShift\nApply modifications\nOverlay research module entries\nHydrate resolvedInstruction
GES --> Client : EffectiveStep[]
Client --> JT : EffectiveStep[]
JT -> JT : Render JourneyTimeline\n+ pause/resume controls\n+ consent chips

== Patient self-view (PatientCareplan) ==

Clinician -> PC : Switch to patient role\n-> /patient
PC -> Client : getPatientJourneys(patientId)
Client --> PC : PatientJourney[]
PC -> PC : Same tab sort and render\n(read-only; no pause/consent controls)

== Dashboard / Worklist — form deduplication ==

JT -> MDS : getMergedDueStepsForPatient(\n  patientId, today\n)
MDS -> Resolver : For each ACTIVE journey:\n  getEffectiveSteps(journey)

loop per Active Journey
  Resolver -> GES : getEffectiveSteps(journey_i)
  GES --> Resolver : EffectiveStep[]
  Resolver -> Resolver : Filter steps where\n  scheduledDate is within\n  today's window
end

Resolver -> Resolver : Deduplicate by templateEntryId\n(keep first occurrence;\ndiscard duplicates from\nparallel journeys)
Resolver --> MDS : MergedDueStep[]\n(no duplicate questionnaires)
MDS --> JT : Merged due steps for\ndashboard/worklist display

note right of Resolver
  Key invariant:
  The same questionnaire
  (templateEntryId) is shown
  at most once per day, even
  when two parallel journeys
  both schedule it.
end note

@enduml
